'''Christopher Guard''' ([[5 December|December 5]], [[1953]]) is an English actor. He voiced [[Frodo Baggins]] in [[The Lord of the Rings (1978 film)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (1978 film)]]. He is the older brother of [[Dominic Guard]], who played [[Peregrin Took]].
